Lit. 'TERRESTRIAL-be on top', i.e. the roof over the underworld from which the ancestors emerged. Cf. the following, with and without the 'TERRESTRIAL' prefix: koni- 'be short', te-koni- 'be shallow'; taša- 'be long', te-taša- 'be deep'; sikɬi- 'scratch', te-sikɬi 'rake the ground'.
This stem takes SG/DU -nne. PL /- ̄ we/, noun inflection. The superscript hyphen is a macron affecting any vowel that precedes /we/.
